{"tid":808104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"瑙魯總統指愛欺負小國 中國反駁：最講究平等","createTime":"2018-09-06T05:41:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T12:55:11.000Z","uid":75969,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4330b9c08df7c9054c336c55040812c75199cb82","tid":808104,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T05:41:30.000Z","msg":"相關報導<br />\n【嬲豬離場】瑙魯辦太平洋論壇 中國代表搶發言被打斷<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/byNbQT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/byNbQT</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_2542458_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_2542458_1.jpg&h=8ad71ac9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔記者鍾麗華／綜合報導〕太平洋島國論壇在我國南太平洋友邦諾魯舉行，中國代表搶發言遭諾魯總統瓦卡制止，以及入境諾魯的外交護照風波，中國外交部發言人華春瑩今天在例行記者會上反批，諾魯此舉是「拙劣鬧劇」。<br />\n<br />\n華春瑩宣稱，中國是以太平洋島國論壇「對話夥伴」出席會議。諾魯做為主辦國，「違背國際慣例和論壇規定，上演了一齣拙劣的鬧劇」，要求中方代表持普通護照入境。在「大多數成員國和中方提出交涉，並表示將抵制會議」下，諾方「不得不同意中方代表團持外交護照與會」。<br />\n<br />\n她聲稱，會議期間，諾方「再次不顧國際會議慣例阻撓中方代表講話」，中方當即提出交涉，並提前離開會場以示抗議，「出席會議的許多國家代表團也離開會場，對諾方表示強烈不滿」。<br />\n<br />\n華春瑩說，任何從事「兩個中國」、「一中一台 」的行徑「都是不得人心的，也是不能得逞的」，「奉勸諾魯認清大勢，糾正錯誤，不要繼續做逆歷史潮流而動的事情」。對於瓦卡指中國是個「欺負小國的大國」，她聲稱，這「純粹是無理取鬧」，中國在國際關係中，「最講究大小國家一律平等」，而唯有自重，才能贏得尊重，「自重自尊與國家大小沒有關係」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2542458\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2542458&d=w5pgVsCMpZrOvdE%2B8kmc8l0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=b3f35a66\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2542458&h=0836c6f6\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2542458</a>"},{"pid":"6458745a0eea167ed68e2d04e87d8b1d4d81cf9e","tid":808104,"uid":18241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T06:23:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06427b07dccab59a7bc8df4db063fe2c9c2649ca","tid":808104,"uid":7632,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:50:48.000Z","msg":"中国揸住支旗咪嗌你地好平等囉"},{"pid":"2f044b833effee5b2bd8145c619126a544c5e95a","tid":808104,"uid":47042,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:56:13.000Z","msg":"講得啱呀，咁撚大個蟈家好似小學雞咁蝦蝦霸霸"},{"pid":"7889c5f5b817775f7a39266cdf8adf9962fa3833","tid":808104,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T08:06:03.000Z","msg":"笑撚到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"704aeeac2ff25c7c31c48261ff047f5d9e135fb7","tid":808104,"uid":54337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T08:09:40.000Z","msg":"搞笑國際冠軍，又贏"},{"pid":"6863396ca80bdafa7db42bd4ed849c33cd6f3d5a","tid":808104,"uid":31098,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T12:55:11.000Z","msg":"&quot;All animals are equal, but some animals are more equal than others.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n-- George Orwell, Animal Farm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}